Popular club owner and show promoter, Pascal Chibuike Okechukwu popularly known as Cubana Chief Priest, has remembered his late mum who believed in him.

The celebrity bar-man shared a throwback photo of his mum and dad while he was still a baby, and lamented about how his dad who disowned him is the one enjoying his money, instead of his mum who believed in him.

According to him, ‘This life no balance’. Read his post below…

“Sacramento Baptismal !!!! E Get As This Life Be, My MaMa Wey Believe Me Die No Come Dey To Enjoy The Fruit Of Her Labour, E Come Be My PaPa Wey Been Disown Me Na Him Come Dey Chop The Whole Glory….This Life No Balance, RIP MaMa Wey Born ”